Laver cookie for children's health
Children's tasty and healthy cookie using natural laver
Excellent texture and easy digestion for young children
The Laver Story
It has plenty of potassium and helps to promote children's bone development.{" "}
It also has plenty of vitamin A which promotes healthy eye, especially for people who frequently use their smart phones and computers.{" "}
Algin, which is abundant in seaweed and has an effect that promotes bowel movements, is good for young children suffering from constipation.
How to enjoy ABC cookie
Check list for babies
Please give the baby enough water with the cookie and watch the baby until finishing eating.
Do not feed the cookie when the baby is lying or there is a chance to block the airway.
If the baby is allergic to a certain ingredient, please check all ingredients carefully.
